RACE.RACE_TEXT: SAM HOUSTON RACE PARK RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 84. Allowance Optional Claiming Purse 11000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON THREE RACES OR CLAIMING PRICE $7,500. Weight, 123 lbs. Claiming Price $7,500.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: AA TAKE A CHANCE chased the pace from the two path while in a steady drive down the back stretch and into the turn, then rallied in the late stretch and was up just in time to succeed. RB MUNCHIE lead the way from the gate and down the backstretch, cleared the far turn, was in gamely drive down the stretch but was out bid by an outer rival and was able to hold the place position. HONEY PROOF tracked the pace while three wide, then menaced on the turn to close well in the late stretch but it was not enough. PROUD AMERICAN bobbled at the start, then settled back along the inside, was in a steady drive throughout the turn, angled out four wide to rally in the late stretch but came up empty. FLEETS ACE AA chased the pace from the inside into the turn and never fired in the stretch. RB BLAIR HOPE tracked the pace between rivals, steadied slightly then kicked up heels before urging down the remainder of the backstretch and into the turn, was out of momentum and had no final bid in the stretch.
